<h2>How to Sign Up</h2>

<div class="frugle_business_point">
	<%= image_tag "filler-large.jpg" %>
	<h3>Find Your Business</h3>
	<p>Search your phone number to find your business.  Chances are we've already listed it.  If not, feel free to  <%= link_to "add it yourself", new_business_path%>, or <a href="mailto:contact@frugle.me">contact us</a> and we'll change that.</p>
</div>

<div class="frugle_business_point">
	<%= image_tag "filler-large.jpg" %>
	<h3>Verify</h3>
	<p>We have to confirm you are the business owner.  We'll autocall you with a special code to verify your listing.</p>
</div>

<div class="frugle_business_point">
	<%= image_tag "filler-large.jpg" %>
	<h3>Login and manage your Frugles</h3>
	<p>Once you verify, we'll send you an email with login information so you can manage your existing Frugles, create your own.</p>
</div>
	
